This directory contains the proprietary, commercially-licensed team/observability tier of
Faraday. It is NOT covered by the Apache-2.0 license that governs the engine. Use requires
a valid commercial license from the copyright holder.

The code here is compiled into a Faraday build ONLY when the `enterprise` build tag is set.
Default open-source builds link none of it. The tier is sold as a self-hosted license +
support that runs inside the air-gap and cannot phone home; license validation is performed
offline against a public key embedded in the binary (see internal/license).

